Que 10: Can we use lambda expressions with any interface? Why or why not?
Ans: No, lambda expressions cannot be used with any interfaces in Java 8.
	Reason - Lambda expression can only be used with functional interfaces.
			A functional inteface is an interface that has only one abstract method.
	
	Why not - A lambda expression provides implementation fpr a single method. 
				So the complier needs, one clear method to map the lambda to,
				If inteface has multiple absract methods, the complier cannot determines which method the lambda is meant for leads to ambiguity.


